ing-implants-sec-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanimal%20experiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20scrutiny%20after%20the%20Physicians%20Committee%20for%20Responsible%20Medicine%20(PCRM)%2C%20a%20medical%20ethics%20group%2C%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20putting%20the%20monkeys%20through%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20suffering%20as%20a%20result%20of%20inadequate%20animal%20care%20and%20the%20highly%20invasive%20experimental%20head%20implants%20during%20the%20experiments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPCRM%20asked%20the%20US%20regulators%20to%20investigate%20Musk%20for%20securities%20fraud%20after%20claiming%20in%20an%20X%20post%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20monkey%20has%20died%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20Neuralink%20implant.%26quot%3B%20Musk%20later%20claimed%20that%20Neuralink's%20facilities%20were%20like%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-neuralink-monkeys-live-in-paradise-denies-gruesome-deaths-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonkey%20paradise%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPCRM%20alleged%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20SEC%20that%20%26quot%3BMusk%20knows%20that%20to%20be%20false.%26quot%3B%20It%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed%20yet%20if%20the%20SEC%20will%20be%20investigating%20Neuralink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20company%20has%20moved%20on%20to%20human%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20livestream%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Arbaugh%20could%20be%20seen%20using%20a%20specialized%20chair%2C%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20a%20laptop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArbaugh%20appeared%20to%20be%20controlling%20a%20game%20of%20chess%20while%20his%20hands%20remained%20on%20the%20armrests%20of%20his%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20playing%20chess%20and%20so%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20ya'll%20have%20enabled%20me%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20I%20wasn't%20able%20to%20really%20do%20much%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20especially%20not%20like%20this%2C%