only%20needed%20to%20imagine%20the%20cursor%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBasically%20it%20was%20like%20using%20the%20force%20on%20a%20cursor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-first-human-trial-patient-quadriplegic-elon-musk-x-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710976956000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fb65f0895d82203032d31c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-first-human-trial-patient-quadriplegic-elon-musk-x-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk's%20Neuralink%20reveals%20first%20human%20trial%20patient%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20quadriplegic%20who%20says%20brain%20chip%20is%20'not%20perfect'%20but%20has%20changed%20his%20life%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A145%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneuralink-first-human-trial-patient-quadriplegic-elon-musk-x-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20unveils%20strict%20car%20emission%20limits%20to%20boost%20EVs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710976799000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F8B67%2Fproduction%2F_132978653_gettyimages-1243226654.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68621430%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20includes%20a%20goal%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20all%20new%20vehicles%20sold%20to%20be%20electric%20by%202032.%20It%20was%207.6%25%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68621430%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68621430.am