%20best%20friend%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20is%20his%20wife%20Kalpana%20Das%20with%20whom%20he%20maintains%20an%20Ayurvedic%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20both%20are%20vegan%2C%20and%20our%20lifestyle%20is%20plant-based.%20I%20think%20whatever%20we%20eat%20affects%20our%20brain.%20I%20think%20your%20fitness%20comes%20from%20within%2C%20from%20within%20yourself%2C%20from%20your%20mind%2C%20from%20your%20heart.%20You%20can%20be%20as%20fit%20as%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20life%20is%20no%20different%20from%20other%20people's%20lives.%20It%20has%20ups%20and%20downs.%20I%20have%20seen%20many%20aspects%20of%20life%20as%20have%20others.%20You%20should%20always%20keep%20hope%20to%20overcome%20any%20problem.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20every%20difficulty%20has%20a%20purpose.%20You%20will%20not%20know%20about%20it%20then%2C%20but%20you%20will%20know%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20shared%20some%20tips%20about%20healthy%20eating.%20%26quot%3BI%20prefer%20to%20eat%20ramdana%20and%20not%20wholegrains.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20sabudana%20khichid%20is%20made%20on%20fasting%20days%2C%20so%20I%20eat%20ramdana.%20I%20have%20been%20fasting%20every%20Monday%20for%20the%20past%2025%20years.%20Ramdana%20is%20a%20must-have%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20light%20food%2C%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20healthiest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20Chief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20have%20a%20cheat%20day%3F%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20ice-cream%20on%20my%20cheat%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHalf%20of%20your%20difficulties%20will%20be%20solved%20if%20you%20keep%20your%20mind%20under%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20began%20serving%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20November%202022%20for%20a%20two-year%20tenure.%20His%20father%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20YV%20Chandrachud%2C%20was%20the%20longest-serving%20Chief%20Justice%20Of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20holds%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%20in%20Economics%20from%20St%20Stephen's%20College.%20He%20later%20completed%20LLB%20from%20Delhi%20University%2C%20and%20LLM%20and%20a%20doctorate%20from%20Harvard%20Law%20School%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710954960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fv69008hg_dy-chandrachud_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhealthy-food-yoga-a-day-in-the-life-of-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-5277496%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20during%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20gave%20a%20peek%20into%20how%20a%20typical%20day%20starts%20for%20him%2C%20one%20of%20the%20custodians%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20For%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20the%20day%20begins%20at%203.30%20am.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhealthy-food-yoga-a-day-in-the-life-of-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-5277496%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhealthy-food-yoga-a-day-in-the-life-of-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-5277496%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhealthy-food-yoga-a-day-in-the-life-of-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-5277496%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Talks%20push%20on%20in%20crisis-wracked%20Haiti%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710954864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108656566%2Cimgsize-1289226.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes