ions%20in%20a%20global%20happiness%20index%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20which%20noted%20that%20older%20age%20is%20associated%20with%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinland%20emerged%20as%20the%20happiest%20country%20in%20the%20world%2C%20topping%20the%20World%20Happiness%20Report%202024%2C%20the%20seventh%20successive%20year%20that%20the%20country%20has%20occupied%20the%20top%20spot%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20of%20the%20top%2010%20countries%20are%20Denmark%2C%20Iceland%2C%20Sweden%2C%20Israel%2C%20Netherlands%2C%20Norway%2C%20Luxembourg%2C%20Switzerland%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20ranked%20126th%20on%20the%20list%2C%20behind%20countries%20such%20as%20Libya%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Palestine%20and%20Niger%2C%20according%20to%20the%20findings%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20mark%20the%20UN's%20International%20Day%20of%20Happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Happiness%20Report%20is%20a%20partnership%20of%20Gallup%2C%20the%20Oxford%20Wellbeing%20Research%20Centre%2C%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Solutions%20Network%2C%20and%20the%20WHR's%20Editorial%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20in%20India%20are%20the%20%26quot%3Bhappiest%26quot%3B%20while%20those%20in%20%26quot%3Blower%20middle%26quot%3B%20rung%20are%20the%20least%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20(23rd)%20has%20fallen%20out%20of%20the%20top%2020%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20the%20World%20Happiness%20Report%20was%20first%20published%20in%202012%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20large%20drop%20in%20the%20well-being%20of%20Americans%20under%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%20remains%20bottom%20of%20the%20overall%20rankings%20as%20the%20world's%20'unhappiest'%20nation.%20Pakistan%20is%20ranked%20108th%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20older%20age%20is%20associated%20with%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20in%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Brefuting%20some%20claims%20that%20the%20positive%20association%20between%20age%20and%20life%20satisfaction%20only%20exists%20in%20high-income%20nations.%26quot%3B%20On%20average%2C%20older%20men%20in%20India%20are%20more%20satisfied%20with%20life%20than%20older%20women%20%26quot%3Bbut%20when%20taking%20all%20other%20measures%20into%20account%2C%20older%20women%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20than%20their%20male%20counterparts%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20older%20adults%20with%20secondary%20or%20higher%20education%20and%20those%20of%20higher%20social%20castes%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20than%20counterparts%20without%20formal%20education%20and%20those%20from%20scheduled%20castes%20and%20scheduled%20tribes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20older%20population%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20worldwide%2C%20with%20140%20million%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20over%2C%20second%20only%20to%20its%20250%20million%20Chinese%20counterparts.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20average%20growth%20rate%20for%20Indians%20aged%2060%20and%20above%20is%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20overall%20population%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatisfaction%20with%20living%20arrangements%2C%20perceived%20discrimination%2C%20and%20self-rated%20health%20emerge%20as%20the%20top%20three%20predictors%20of%20life%20satisfaction%20for%20India%20in%20this%20study%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20found%20that%20older%20men%2C%20those%20in%20the%20higher%20age%20groups%2C%20currently%20married%2C%20and%20those%20who%20were%20educated%2C%20report%20higher%20life%20satisfaction%20compared%20to%20their%20respective%20peers.%20Lower%20satisfaction%20with%20living%20arrangements%2C%20perceived%20discrimination%2C%20and%20poor%20self-rated%20health%20were%20important%20factors%20associated%20with%20low%20life%20satisfaction%20among%20older%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20findings%20of%20this%20study%20indicate%20that%20strengthening%20family%20networks%20to%20ensure%20a%20comfortable%20living%20arrangement%20for%20older%20adults%2C%20men%2C%20widowed%2C%20and%20those%20without%20formal%20education%20in%20particular%2C%20and%20bolstering%20social%20networks%20to%20reduce%20discrimination%20may%20enhance%20well-being%20in%20older%20age%2C%20it%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20Serbia%20(37th)%20and%20Bulgaria%20(81st)%20have%20had%20the%20biggest%20increases%20in%20average%20life%20evaluation%20scores%20since%20they%20were%20first%20measured%20by%20the%20Gallup%20World%20Poll%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20two%20countries%20showing%20the%20largest%20increases%20in%20life%20evaluations%20are%20Latvia%20(46th)%20and%20Congo%20(Brazzaville)%20(89th)%2C%20with%20rank%20increases%20of%2044%20and%2040%20places%2C%20respectively%2C%20between%202013%20and%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20report%20gives%20separate%20rankings%20by%20age%20group%2C%20in%20many%20cases%20varying%20widely%20from%20the%20overall%20rankings.%20Lithuania%20tops%20the%20list%20for%20children%20and%20young%20people%20under%2030%2C%20while%20Denmark%20is%20the%20world's%20happiest%20nation%20for%20those%2060%20and%20older.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710953700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fftr76vck_india-population_625x300_29_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffinland-is-worlds-happiest-country-for-7th-time-straight-india-stands-at-5278059%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20was%20ranked%20126th%20out%20of%20143%20nations%20in%20a%20global%20happiness%20index%20released%20on%20Wednesday%20which%20noted%20