ith-lots-of-ghee-orry-drops-a-fun-vlog-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F108656287.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%20-%20%26quot%3BMy%20Mission%20Is%20Use%20Of%20Technology%20In%20Courts%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20technology%20in%20judicial%20work%2C%20which%20takes%20it%20to%20the%20common%20man%20and%20helps%20bring%20faith%20on%20the%20legal%20system%20is%20a%20task%20he%20has%20taken%20as%20his%20mission%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20told%20NDTV%20today.%20In%20an%20exclusive%2C%20overarching%20interview%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20also%20discussed%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20district%20courts%2C%20reassuring%20the%20common%20man%20about%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20law%2C%20his%20dietary%20preferences%20and%20everything%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20feel%20that%20all%20citizens%20have%20a%20vital%20stake%20in%20understanding%20what%20work%20is%20done%20by%20the%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%C2%A0%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20because%20at%20one%20level%2C%20the%20institutions%20run%20from%20public%20revenue%20so%20the%20people%20have%20a%20right%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20beyond%20that%2C%20I%20think%20common%20citizens%20will%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20faith%20and%20confidence%20in%20the%20work%20which%20we%20do%20as%20courts%20once%20they%20realise%20the%20seriousness%20with%20which%20even%20the%20smallest%20of%20issues...%20the%20court%20has%20to%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20could%20include%20someone's%20pension%2C%20loss%20of%20job%2C%20a%20case%20or%20arson%20or%20someone%20in%20jail%20without%20parole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20each%20of%20these%20issues%20very%20seriously.%20It%20is%20one%20thing%20for%20common%20citizens%20to%20see%20what%20is%20happening%20and%20very%20different%20to%20read%20what%20is%20happening%20when%20you%20see%20something%2C%20you%20understand%20what%20the%20courts%20are%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20aspect%20of%20this%20is%20ensuring%20that%20no%20one%20is%20left%20behind%2C%20even%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%20with%20its%20technological%20divide.%20He%20said%20he%20has%20been%20chairing%20a%20project%20to%20open%20E-seva%20kendras%20across%20districts%20that%20makes%20all%20of%20this%20accessible%20to%20the%20common%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20on%20February%2029%C2%A0%20this%20year%2C%203.09%20crore%20cases%20have%20been%20heard%20on%20video-conferencing%20mode%20all%20over%20the%20country%20--%20in%20high%20courts%20and%20district%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reassure%20the%20district%20courts%20and%20sort%20out%20their%20problems%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20also%20undertaken%20to%20ramp%20up%20the%20dialogue%20%E2%80%93%20through%20pan-India%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20of%20one%20such%20conference%20held%20recently%20that%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20over%20250%20district%20judges%2C%20he%20said%20it%20was%20a%20learning%20experience%20since%20district%20courts%20are%20in%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20through%20these%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20begin%20to%20learn%20a%20lot%20more%20about%20the%20problems%20of%20the%20stakeholders%20in%20our%20system%20--%20litigants%2C%20lawyers%20who%20come%20to%20court%2C%20marginalised%20groups%20who%20seek%20access%20to%20justice%2C%20women%20-%20what%20kind%20of%20issues%20they%20have%20when%20they%20have%20a%20case%20in%20a%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20the%20forerunner%20of%20a%20larger%20conference%20of%20over%201%2C000%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710953520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjm9dqk0c_dy-chandrachud_625x300_20_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-mission-in-use-of-technology-in-courts-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-exclusive-5277450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20use%20of%20technology%20in%20judicial%20work%2C%20which%20takes%20it%20to%20the%20common%20man%20and%20helps%20bring%20faith%20on%20the%20legal%20system%20is%20a%20task%20he%20has%20taken%20as%20his%20mission%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20told%20NDTV%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-mission-in-use-of-technology-in-courts-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-exclusive-5277450%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-mission-in-use-of-technology-in-courts-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-exclusive-5277450%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmy-mission-in-use-of-technology-in-courts-chief-justice-of-india-dy-chandrachud-exclusive-5277450%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NDTV%20Exclusive%20-%20%26quot%3BNo%20Case%20Too%20Small%20For%20Highest%20Court%26quot%3B%3A%20Chief%20Justice's%20Message%20To%20Citizens%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20always%20there%20for%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Birrespective%20of%20wealth%2C%20social%20status%2C%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20or%20gender%20or%20who%20is%20in%20power%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20case%20is%20too%20small%20for%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20told%20NDTV's%20Ashish%20Bhargava%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20wide-ranging%20discussion%20focused%20on%20the%20use%20of%20technology%20to%20ensure%20men%20and%20women%20across%20the%20country%20can%20access%20every%20level%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20give%20this%20message%20to%20all%20-%20we%20are%20always%20there%20for%20the%20common%20citizens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20I%20get%20e-mails%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night.%20Once%20there%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20needed%20medical%20termination%20of%20a%20pregnancy...%20my%20staff%20contacted%20me%20and%20we%20constituted%20a%20bench%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EKisi%20ka%20ghar%20demolish%20ho%20gaya...%20kisi%20ko%20usi%20ke%20ghar%20se%20bahar%20nikaal%20diya...%20kisi%20ko%20surrender%20karna%20hai%20lekin%20vo%20beemar%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(someone's%20house%20may%20have%20been%20demolished...%20someone%20may%20have%20been%20thrown%20out%20of%20their%20house...%20someone%20may%20need%20to%20surrender%20but%20they%20are%20unwell)...%20all%20these%20heart-breaking%20cases%20are%20given%20the%20serious%20attention%20of%20the%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20case%20which%20is%20too%20small...%20we%20treat%20everyone%20equally%20and%20our%20mission%20is%20to%20stand%20by%20the%20common%20people.%20We%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20regardless%20of%20who%20is%20in%20power%2C%20common%20people%20have%20concerns%20and%20the%20judiciary%20is%20the%20vital%20element%20in%20the%20preservation%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20of%20the%20courts%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20fabric%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20and%20gives%20it%20a%20vital%20legitimacy.%20That%2C%20he%20explained%2C%20was%20why%20he%20reached%20out%20to%20district%20courts%20and%20met%20judges%20at%20a%20recently%20organised%20conference%20in%20Gujarat's%20Kutch%2C%20in%20which%20150%20judges%20took%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20common%20citizen%20faces%20any%20problem%2C%20s%2Fhe%20first%20goes%20to%20a%20district%20court.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20important%20to%20meet%20these%20judges.%20You%20see%2C%20when%20we%20strengthen%20the%20district-level%20courts%20we%20also%20strengthen%20the%20connection%20of%20the%20people%20with%20the%20judiciary%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20listened%20to%20their%20views%20there...%20so%20we%20can%20change%20our%20policy-making%20and%20connect%20with%20the%20people%20through%20these%20judges%2C%20who%20have%20a%20direct%20interface%20with%20common%20citizens.%20We%20get%20to%20learn%20a%20lot%20more%20about%20the%20problems%20of%20stakeholders%20in%20our%20system%20-%20marginalised%20people%2C%20women%20seeking%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20conference%20of%20over%20a%20thousand%20judges%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20India%20must%20have%20%26quot%3Ba%20sense%20of%20faith%20and%20confidence%20in%20the%20work%20we%20do%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20once%20they%20realise%20the%20seriousness%20with%20which%20even%20the%20smallest%20of%20issues...%20smallest%20not%20for%20us...%20but%20small%20like%20someone's%20pension%2C%20a%20misconceived%20FIR%2C%20someone%20who%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20for%20several%20years...%20we%20take%20all%20these%20cases%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20greatest%20strength%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20and%20all%20the%20district%20courts%20are%20%26quot%3Bpeople's%20courts%26quot%3B.%20All%20of%20these%20were%20created%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20all%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20personal%20note%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20gave%20an%20insight%20into%20his%20busy%20day%2C%20which%20begins%20at%20an%20eye-watering%203.30%20am%2C%20when%20the%20environment%20around%20his%20is%20calm%20and%20he%20can%20focus%20on%20his%20yoga.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20best%20friend%20is%20my%20wife%20(Kalpana%20Chandrachud).%20She%20and%20I%20follow%20an%20ayurvedic%20diet.%20We%20are%20vegan...%20I%20think%20whatever%20we%20eat%20affects%20our%20brain.%20I%20think%20your%20fitness%20comes%20from%20within...%20from%20your%20mind%20and%20heart.%20You%20can%20be%20as%20fit%20as%20you%20want...%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20does%20the%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20who%20also%20has%20a%20strict%20diet%20that%20revolves%20around%20a%20grain%20called%20ramdana%2C%20have%20a%20guilty%20secret%3F%20Yes.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20ice%20cream%20on%20my%20cheat%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20chuckled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710953520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fqacbhhj_cji-to-ndtv-_625x300_20_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchief-justice-dy-chandrachud-ndtv-interview-no-case-too-small-for-highest-court-chief-justices-message-to-citizens-5277167%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20always%20there%20for%20citizens%20of%20India%2C%20%26quot%3Birrespective%20of%20wealth%2C%20social%20status%2C%20caste%2C%20religion%2C%20or%20gender%20or%20who%20is%20in%20power%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bno%20case%20is%20too%20small%20for%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-ne