.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcci-denies-interim-order-restricting-google-from-charging-its-service-fee-124032001020_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boy%2C%209%2C%20Showed%20%26quot%3BNo%20Emotion%26quot%3B%20After%20Killing%20Animals%20At%20Dutch%20Zoo%2C%20Says%20Staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%209-year-old%20boy%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20strangled%20several%20animals%20to%20death%20during%20a%20solo%20trip%20to%20a%20petting%20zoo.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20March%2011%20at%20the%20Rekerhout%20petting%20zoo%20in%20Alkmaar%2C%20Netherlands.%20The%20boy%2C%20whose%20identity%20hasn't%20been%20revealed%2C%20travelled%20alone%20to%20the%20zoo%20and%20killed%20up%20to%20nine%20rabbits%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs%20with%20no%20apparent%20motive.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20shown%20%26quot%3Bno%20emotion%26quot%3B%20after%20he%20carried%20out%20the%20senseless%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20you%20completely%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20zoo%20manager%20Ali%20Dorenbos%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F03%2F20%2Fhorror-boy-9-strangles-rabbits-guinea-pigs-death-zoo-20496611%2F%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Police%20caught%20the%20child%20and%20his%20parents%20were%20called%20to%20the%20scene.%20He%20will%20not%20face%20criminal%20charges%20as%20he%20is%20under%20the%20age%20of%2012%2C%20but%20he%20will%20be%20enrolled%20into%20a%20care%20programme%2C%20cops%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20sorry%20for%20the%20animals%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20little%20boy%20who%20apparently%20feels%20so%20bad%20that%20he%20has%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20psychiatrist%2C%20Esther%20van%20Fenema%2C%20said%20of%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20kill%20an%20animal%20in%20the%20house%3B%20explain%20to%20the%20child%20why.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%20an%20insect.%20So%20that%20it%20learns%20that%20you%20don't%20wring%20the%20neck%20of%20a%20guinea%20pig%2C%20which%20is%20harmful%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20psychiatrist%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-news%2Fpetting-zoo-horror-primary-school-32393045%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMirror%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20specialist%20Anne-Marie%20Le%20Buhan%20of%20the%20Het%20Geitenweitje%20Foundation%20in%20Laren%2C%20also%20commented%20on%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BHorrible.%20How%3F%20This%20is%20very%20extreme.%20And%20was%20there%20no%20supervision%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Freal-estate-agent-in-australia-accidentally-burns-down-property-worth-rs-24-crore-5275141%5C%22%3EReal%20Estate%20Agent%20In%20Australia%20Accidentally%20Burns%20Down%20Property%20Worth%20%E2%82%B9%2024%20Crore%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20this%20incident%20reportedly%20comes%20after%20it%20was%20revealed%20children%20are%20filming%20themselves%20using%20catapults%20to%20injure%20and%20kill%20animals%20in%20a%20UK-wide%20WhatsApp%20chat.%20Around%20500%20members%20across%20110%20group%20chats%20have%20shared%20footage%20of%20their%20killings%2C%20Metro%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20showed%20injured%20animals%20slowly%20dying%20as%20they%20were%20shot%20with%20the%20catapults%2C%20while%20others%20were%20kicked%20to%20death.%20Animals%20targeted%20include%20pigs%2C%20deer%2C%20pigeons%2C%20foxes%2C%20squirrels%2C%20pheasants%2C%20rabbits%2C%20geese%20and%20ducks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPsychologist%20Joni%20E.%20Johnston%20wrote%20of%20the%20warning%20signs%20parents%20should%20watch%20out%20for%20if%20their%20child%20is%20hurting%20animals.%20%26quot%3BLocking%20a%20pet%20inside%20a%20closed%20space%2C%20violently%20lashing%20out%20at%20a%20pet%20after%20getting%20in%20trouble%20with%20a%20parent%2C%20or%20taking%20pleasure%20in%20w