nd%20Information%20Technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20hereby%20notifies%20the%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20under%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20as%20the%20fact%20check%20unit%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20the%20said%20sub-clause%2C%20in%20respect%20of%20any%20business%20of%20the%20Central%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notification%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Fact%20Check%20Unit%20will%20be%20the%20nodal%20agency%20to%20tackle%20or%20alert%20about%20all%20fake%20news%20or%20misinformation%20related%20to%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20came%20days%20after%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20declined%20to%20restrain%20the%20Centre%20from%20notifying%20the%20unit.%20The%20petition%20was%20filed%20by%20stand-up%20comedian%20Kunal%20Kamra%20and%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20verdict%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20expected%20to%20come%20up%20for%20hearing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(Meity)%20issued%20the%202023%20Rules%2C%20which%20further%20amended%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Rules%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20if%20the%20fact%20check%20unit%20comes%20across%20or%20is%20informed%20about%20any%20posts%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bfake%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20or%20contain%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20facts%20pertaining%20to%20the%20business%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20would%20flag%20it%20to%20the%20social%20media%20intermediaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20intermediaries%20would%20then%20have%20to%20take%20down%20such%20content%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20retain%20their%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20harbour%26quot%3B%20(legal%20immunity%20against%20third-party%20content).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20check%20unit%20under%20PIB%20was%20established%20in%20November%202019%20with%20a%20stated%20objective%20of%20acting%20as%20a%20deterrent%20to%20creators%20and%20disseminators%20of%20fake%20news%20and%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20provides%20people%20with%20an%20easy%20avenue%20to%20report%20suspicious%20and%20questionable%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20is%20mandated%20to%20counter%20misinformation%20on%20government%20policies%2C%20initiatives%20and%20schemes%20either%20suo%20motu%20or%20under%20a%20reference%20via%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unit%20actively%20monitors%2C%20detects%2C%20and%20counters%20disinformation%20campaigns%2C%20ensuring%20that%20false%20information%20about%20the%20government%20is%20promptly%20exposed%20and%20corrected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710951600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fm1pp5ff_fake-news-generic-pixabay_625x300_07_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-notifies-pib-as-official-fact-checker-for-online-content-5277874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20on%20Wednesday%20notified%20the%20fact%20check%20unit%20under%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%20to%20monitor%20online%20content%20pertaining%20to%20the%20government%20for%20accuracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-notifies-pib-as-official-fact-checker-for-online-content-5277874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-notifies-pib-as-official-fact-checker-for-online-content-5277874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-notifies-pib-as-official-fact-checker-for-online-content-5277874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTake%20Stringent%20Action%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20To%20Poll%20Body%20On%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20'Shakti'%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20Wednesday%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bfight%20against%20a%20shakti%26quot%3B%20remarks%20at%20a%20recent%20rally%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bstringent%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader%20and%20issue%20directions%20for%20lodging%20an%20FIR%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20poll%20panel%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Puri%20and%20Om%20Pathak%20alleged%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3Bfight%20against%20a%20shakti%26quot%3B%20remarks%20were%20rendered%20with%20%26quot%3Bmalicious%20intention%26quot%3B%20of%20insulting%20the%20religious%20values%20associated%20with%20'shakti'%20and%20creating%20enmity%20among%20religions%20to%20appease%20%26quot%3Bsome%20religious%20community%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20statement%20made%20by%20Gandhi%20wherein%20he%20says%20that%20the%20fight%20is%20with%20Shakti%20was%20made%20with%20a%20malicious%20intention%20to%20hurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20Hindus.%20A%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus%20in%20India%20offer%20prayers%20to%20Shakti%20in%20Hinduism%20to%20the%20extent%20there%20exists%20a%20Shakti%20sect%20who%20refer%20to%20the%20Devi%20as%20Shakti%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGandhi's%20call%20to%20fight%20against%20Shakti%20in%20Hinduism%2C%20directly%20implies%20that%20the%20Congress%20supporters%20should%20fight%20against%20the%20worshipping%20deities%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20which%20creates%20hatred%20against%20Hinduism%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20Mumbai%20rally%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20on%20Monday%20clarified%20that%20he%20was%20not%20talking%20about%20any%20religious%20power%20but%20the%20'shakti'%20of%20unrighteousness%2C%20corruption%20and%20falsehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20twisting%20his%20words%20and%20said%20he%20was%20speaking%20about%20the%20power%20of%20which%20Modi%20was%20wearing%20the%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20also%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20made%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20mischievous%26quot%3B%20claims%20with%20regard%20the%20authenticity%20of%20electoral%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20while%20addressing%20the%20Mumbai%20rally%20and%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20Election%20Commission%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20demanded%20that%20the%20poll%20panel%20take%20action%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20remarks%20about%20EVMs%2C%20contending%20that%20such%20kind%20of%20%26quot%3Bdisinformation%20and%20misinformation%26quot%3B%20without%20verification%20of%20facts%20was%20%26quot%3Bprejudicial%26quot%3B%20to%20national%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20made%20such%20remarks%20about%20EVMs%20and%20the%20poll%20panel%20with%20an%20%26quot%3Bintention%20to%20create%20public%20disorder%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20raising%20these%20kinds%20of%20allegations%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20are%20insulting%20the%20electorate%20of%20India.%20Furthermore%2C%20it%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20that%20in%20the%20same%20event%2C%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20blatantly%20denounced%20EVMs%20as%20a%20thief%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20said%20in%20their%20petition%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20demanded%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20take%20%26quot%3Bstringent%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20also%20%26quot%3Bprosecute%26quot%3B%20him%20for%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20stringent%20action%20and%20direct%20lodging%20of%20an%20FIR%20and%20prosecute%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20may%20be%20instructed%20to%20offer%20an%20unconditional%20public%20apology%20and%20retraction%20for%20his%20utterances%20at%20Shivaji%20Park%20event%20in%20Mumbai%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20urged%20in%20their%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIssue%20a%20direction%20to%20INC%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20refrain%20from%20posting%2C%20publishing%2C%20advertising%20and%20propagating%20the%20said%20false%20information%20through%20any%20and%20all%20means%20of%20communication%20either%20spoken%2C%20written%2C%20audio%2Fvirtually%20representation%20or%20otherwise%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20also%20urged%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20direct%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20to%20take%20down%20the%20video%20of%20the%20event%2C%20addressed%20by%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bsubsequent%20tweets%20and%20similar%20tweets%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20same%20content%20by%20other%20Congress%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20poll%20panel%20direct%20the%20platform%20to%20suspend%20the%20official%20handle%20of%20the%20Congress%20%26quot%3Bfor%20spreading%20fake%20news%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTake%20cognizance%20of%20this%20egregious%20violation%20of%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20and%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%20and%20ensure%20that%20such%20offences%20are%20never%20repeated%20in%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20leaders%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bmisinformation%20propagated%20by%20Gandhi%2C%20including%20lies%20about%20the%20EVM%20machines%20despite%20authoritative%20pronouncements%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%26quot%3B%20can%20have%20significant%20consequences%20with%20respect%20to%20the%20trust%20of%20the%20citizen%20in%20the%20election%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20threats%20are%20especially%20perilous%20in%20today's%20age%20since%20these%20falsehoods%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20spread%20rapidly%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20platforms%20unwilling%20or%20unable%20to%20intervene%2C%20fuelling%20threats%20to%20election%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710951420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ftmr4b8mg_rahul-gandhi-_625x300_20_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftake-stringent-action-bjp-to-poll-body-on-rahul-gandhis-shakti-remark-5277859%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20Wednesday%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20against%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bfight%20against%20a%20shakti%26quot%3B%20remarks%20at%20a%20recent%20rally%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20take%20%26quot%3Bstringent%20action%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20Congress%20leader.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftake-stringent-action-bjp-to-poll-body-on-rahul-gandhis-shakti-remark-5277859%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftake-stringent-action-bjp-to-poll-body-on-rahul-gandhis-shakti-remark-5277859%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftake-stringent-action-bjp-to-poll-body-on-rahul-gandhis-shakti-remark-5277859%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20rescuers%20scramble%20to%20save%20