%20a%20recent%20video%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Ashwin%20revealed%20what%20followed%20after%20he%20received%20the%20news%20of%20the%20hospitalisation%20and%20how%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20gesture%20left%20him%20'gobsmacked'.%20He%20even%20went%20on%20to%20call%20Rohit%20an%20%26quot%3Boutstanding%20leader%26quot%3B%20for%20how%20he%20handled%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20how%20she%20was%20and%20if%20she%20was%20conscious.%20The%20doctor%20apparently%20told%20me%20that%20she%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20be%20seen.%20I%20started%20tearing%20up.%20I%20was%20searching%20for%20a%20flight%20but%20I%20couldn't%20get%20one.%20The%20Rajkot%20airport%20closes%20down%20at%206%20as%20there%20are%20no%20flights%20from%20there%20after%206.%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20Rohit%20(Sharma)%20and%20Rahul%20(Dravid)%20Bhai%20came%20to%20my%20room%20and%20Rohit%20literally%20asked%20me%20to%20stop%20thinking%20and%20leave%20to%20be%20there%20with%20my%20family.%20And%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20arrange%20a%20charter%20flight%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKamlesh%2C%20the%20team%20physio%2C%20is%20a%20very%20good%20friend%20of%20mine.%20Rohit%20told%20him%20to%20fly%20with%20me%20to%20Chennai%20and%20be%20with%20me%20but%20I%20convinced%20him%20to%20stay%20back.%20When%20I%20went%20down%2C%20the%20security%20and%20Kamlesh%20were%20already%20there%2C%20waiting.%20Kamlesh%20got%20a%20call%20from%20Rohit%20on%20our%20ride%20towards%20the%20airport%2C%20checking%20up%20on%20me%20and%20literally%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20with%20me%20during%20this%20tough%20time.%20It%20was%209%3A30%20at%20night.%20I%20was%20just%20gobsmacked.%20I%20cannot%20even%20think%20about%20it.%20The%20two%20people%20there%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20that%20I%20could%20talk.%20What%20if%20nobody%20was%20there%3F%20I%20just%20thought%2C%20even%20if%20I%20were%20a%20captain%2C%20I'd%20tell%20my%20players%20to%20go%20