gh%2067%20countries%2C%20and%20their%20experience%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20everyone%20in%20the%20world%20expects%20me%20to%20say%20'Don't%20go%20to%20India'%2C%20but%20life%20is%20far%20more%20complicated%20than%20that.%20What%20happened%20to%20me%20in%20India%20could%20have%20happened%20anywhere%20else.%20Not%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20a%20couple%20travelling%20in%20Belize%2C%20in%20Central%20America%2C%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman%20told%20%3Cem%3ESCMP%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20advice%20to%20women%20is%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%2C%20travel%20and%20do%20so%20without%20fear.%20If%20you%20are%20going%20to%20camp%2C%20it%20should%20be%20in%20a%20place%20not%20too%20far%20from%20the%20road%20where%20you%20can%20easily%20call%20for%20help%20and%20have%20a%20signal%20for%20your%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20partner%20said%20they%20don't%20know%20if%20they%20will%20be%20called%20to%20testify%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20have%20to%2C%20we%20will%2C%20but%20perhaps%20it%20can%20be%20done%20using%20a%20video%20call.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20taking%20responsibility%20for%20being%20a%20risk%20taker%2C%20the%20woman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20understand%20how%20some%20people%20might%20reach%20that%20conclusion.%20You%20know%2C%20society%20convinces%20us%20to%20live%20one%20way%2C%20to%20go%20to%20work%2C%20to%20have%20two%20children%2C%20to%20stay%20in%20our%20circle.%20So%20when%20a%20person%20exits%20their%20circle%2C%20they%20are%20considered%20risk-takers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20left%20the%20house%2C%20and%20yes%2C%20I%20took%20risks%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20regret%20it.%20I%20don't%20regret%20going%20to%20India.%20I%20don't%20regret%20anything%20about%20our%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20if%20we%20had%20just%20gone%20another%20way%20or%20stayed%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20this%20never%20would%20have%20happened.%20But%20using%20the%20same%20logic%2C%20maybe%20something%20worse%20would%20have%20happened%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20alive.%20Accidents%20can%20happen%20anywhere%2C%20even%20inside%20the%20safety%20of%20your%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2028-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%2C%20however%2C%20added%20that%20they%20intend%20to%20continue%20their%20bike%20trips.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20taking%20a%20break%20in%20Spain.%20We%20don't%20know%20when%20but%20we%20are%20sure%20we%20will%20continue.%20We've%20already%20started%20planning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20days%20after%20the%20incident%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-says-probe-on-in-spanish-tourists-gang-rape-case-several-arrested-5201855%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bunder%20investigation%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20several%20people%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710944460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fsrapotl8_spanish-tourist-in-india_625x300_20_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happened-to-me-in-india-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5277086%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20woman%20and%20her%20partner%20are%20now%20back%20in%20Spain.%20They%20said%20they%20don't%20know%20if%20they%20will%20be%20called%20to%20testify%20in%20court%20in%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happened-to-me-in-india-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5277086%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happened-to-me-in-india-spanish-tourist-gang-raped-in-jharkhand-5277086%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-happened-t