0cacophony%20one%20comes%20across%20in%20such%20housing%20complexes.%20The%20evenings%20were%20especially%20vibrant%3A%20kids%20playing%20and%20screaming%2C%20adults%20chatting%20and%20whispering%2C%20bikes%20spluttering%20and%20rickshaws%20honking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELuckily%20I%20was%20there%20also%20on%20January%2026.%20It%20was%20quite%20festive%2C%20and%20many%20events%20had%20been%20organised%20to%20commemorate%20Republic%20Day.%20All%20through%20the%20afternoon%20and%20evening%20kids%20were%20dancing%20and%20singing%20and%20showing%20off%20many%20kinds%20of%20talents.%20One%20particular%20performance%20that%20January%20day%20was%20especially%20striking.%20A%20little%20boy%2C%20maybe%20around%2010%20years%20of%20age%2C%20belted%20out%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20new%20recruit%20in%20the%20hefty%20pantheon%20of%20Indian%20patriotic%20songs.%20With%20much%20gusto%20and%20emotion%2C%20he%20crooned%20multiple%20stanzas%20of%2C%20well%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDesh%20ke%20gaddaron%20ko%2C%20goli%20maaro%20salon%20ko.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20a%20jarring%20moment%2C%20although%20perhaps%20only%20to%20the%20few%20folks%20in%20the%20housing%20complex%20who%20recognised%20the%20venality%20involved%20in%20making%20a%20kid%20sing%20that%20%E2%80%9Csong%E2%80%9D.%20But%20it%20was%20also%20befitting%20the%20so-called%20New%20India.%20A%2010-year-old%20child%20grittily%20singing%20%E2%80%93%20obviously%20trained%20and%20encouraged%20by%20his%20parents%20%E2%80%93%20of%20murdering%20other%20Indians%20(%E2%80%9Ctraitors%E2%80%9D)%20as%20a%20patriotic%20duty%2C%20was%20appropriately%20symbolic%20of%20the%20annihilation%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20values%20on%20a%20day%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20commemorate%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20all%20the%20weird%20discomfort%20of%20that%20day%2C%20the%20experience%20took%20me%20back%20to%20some%20fond%20childhood%20memories.%20Firstly%2C%20I%20felt%20thankful%20to%20my%20good%20fortune%2C%20for%20growing%20up%20I%20had%20not%20been%20exposed%20to%20and%20absorbed%20such%20normalisation%20of%20violence%20and%20bigotry.%20Then%20I%20especially%20remembered%20Himesh%20Sir%2C%20my%20English%20teacher%2C%20and%20his%20endearing%20eccentricities.%20If%20he%20were%20in%20charge%2C%20he%20would%20have%20completely%20jettisoned%20all%20the%20patriotic%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshowbaazi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20involved%20in%20January%2026%20and%20August%2015.%20He%20would%20have%20let%20students%20just%20play%20and%20have%20fun%2C%20or%20perhaps%20not%20even%20bother%20coming%20to%20school%20and%20just%20eat%20jalebis%20at%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F03081550%2F20230201-brahmos_launcher_army_green_republic_day-wikicommons-ac-1024x673.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F03081550%2F20230201-brahmos_launcher_army_green_republic_day-wikicommons-ac-1024x673.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F03081550%2F20230201-brahmos_launcher_army_green_republic_day-wikicommons-ac-300x197.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F03081550%2F20230201-brahmos_launcher_army_green_republic_day-wikicommons-ac.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-638857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22552%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20Brahmos%20launcher%20during%20a%20rehearsal%20for%20the%20India%E2%80%99s%202011%20Republic%20Day%20Parade.%20In%202021%2C%20an%20India%20Brahmos%20missile%20test%20misfired%20into%20Pakistani%20territory%2C%20sparking%20concerns%20of%20escalation%20between%20the%20rival%20nuclear%20powers.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHimesh%20Sir%20was%20a%20brilliant%20educator%20apart%20from%20being%20a%20highly%20idiosyncratic%20individual.%20For%20example%2C%20for%20some%20weird%20reason%20he%20had%20the%20first%20page%20of%20philosopher%20Bertrand%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20autobiography%20fully%20memorised.%20That%20page%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%98What%20I%20Have%20Lived%20For%E2%80%99%2C%20was%2C%20and%20is%2C%20just%20permanently%20etched%20in%20his%20memory%3A%20even%20as%20recently%20as%20in%202022%2C%20he%20recited%20all%20320%20words%20of%20it%20to%20a%20group%20of%20us%20friends%20as%20part%20of%20the%20answer%20to%20our%20question%2C%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESir%2C%20how%20did%20you%20come%20to%20love%20the%20English%20language%20so%20much%3F%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20Himesh%20Sir%20who%20introduced%20me%20to%20Russell%20and%20other%20great%20thinkers%20and%20writers%20when%20I%20was%20a%20kid.%20He%20helped%20me%20discover%20the%20intoxicating%20world%20of%20books%20and%20the%20power%20of%20knowledge.%20Like%20in%20many%20other%20cities%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20streets%20and%20footpaths%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20cities%20have%20always%20been%20a%20paradise%20for%20book%20lovers%2C%20with%20low-cost%20copies%20of%20all%20kinds%20of%20books%20on%20sale%20if%20one%20knew%20where%20to%20look.%20Sir%20would%20often%20talk%20about%20these%20open-air%20bookstores%20during%20his%20classes%2C%20telling%20us%20how%20he%20bought%20this%20awesome%20book%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20rupees%20only%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20magnificent%20volume%20for%20%E2%80%9Cfive%20rupees%20only%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai%20and%20Pune.%20In%20his%20house%20Himesh%20Sir%20had%20a%20massive%20collection%20of%20books%2C%20mostly%20bought%20from%20such%20booksellers%20and%20from%20stores%20like%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fmumbais-iconic-strand-book-stall-shuts-shop-personal-touch-will-missed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStrand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20which%20he%20was%20extremely%20fond%20of.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMuch%20of%20my%20childhood%20and%20early%20teenage%20period%20was%20spent%20leafing%20through%20his%20collections%20and%20reading%20many%20of%20his%20recommended%20books.%20C.E.M.%20Joad%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Story%20of%20Civilization%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20among%20my%20favourites%2C%20and%20I%20have%20always%20loved%20Joad%E2%80%99s%20definition%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98civilised%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%9Cmaking%20and%20liking%20beautiful%20things%2C%20thinking%20freely%2C%20and%20living%20rightly%20and%20maintaining%20justice%20equally%20between%20%5Bhu%5Dman%20and%20%5Bhu%5Dman%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESir%20was%20also%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20the%20iconic%20English%20grammar%20book%20often%20just%20called%20%E2%80%98the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dnaindia.com%2Fanalysis%2Fcolumn-looking-for-my-copy-of-wren-martin-1273151%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWren%20and%20Martin%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99.%20I%20happened%20to%20have%20a%20withering%20old%20copy%20of%20it%20gifted%20to%20me%20by%20an%20Anglo-Indian%20elderly%20neighbour.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWren%20and%20Martin%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20a%20large%20number%20of%20passages%20and%20poems%20from%20English%20literature%20dotted%20throughout%20its%20hundreds%20of%20pages%2C%20and%20even%20though%20I%20never%20studied%20literature%20or%20read%20the%20classics%20(in%20any%20language)%2C%20I%20became%20aware%20of%20and%20admired%20the%20beauty%20and%20profundity%20of%20great%20writing%20because%20of%20this%20and%20other%20books%20I%20studied%20through%20Himesh%20Sir%E2%80%99s%20prodding%20and%20encouragement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-1024x410.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-1024x410.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F26110550%2FIMG_2635.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-669939%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22336%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEver%20since%20that%20Republic%20Day%20experience%2C%20my%20mind%20frequently%20travels%20to%20all%20these%20memories%20when%20I%20think%20of%20what%20kids%20today%20are%20reading%20(and%20singing)%2C%20and%20the%20kinds%20of%20ideas%20they%20are%20being%20exposed%20to.%20As%20a%20child%20I%20often%20heard%20adults%20employing%20the%20Marathi%20proverb%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%20%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B2%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20%E2%80%98r%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eeading%20will%20save%20you%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%99%20Today%20I%20wonder%20how%20much%20relevance%20this%20saying%20has%2C%20considering%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20kids%2C%20teenagers%2C%20and%20young%20adults%20are%20reading%20are%20WhatsApp%20messages%2C%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20and%20generally%20awful%20and%20hateful%20propaganda%20masquerading%20as%20history%2C%20news%2C%20and%20expert%20opinion.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Instagram-bred%20youth%20anyway%2C%20for%20quite%20a%20while%20now%2C%20have%20been%20doing%20less%20of%20reading%20and%20more%20of%20%E2%80%98consuming%E2%80%99.%20A%20part%20of%20me%20understands%20that%20my%20discomfort%20with%20these%20developments%20might%20just%20be%20the%20inevitable%20and%20often%20annoying%20fondness%20one%20develops%2C%20as%20one%20ages%2C%20for%20how%20things%20were%20in%20the%20past.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20is%20true%20that%20we%20simply%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20banality%20of%20evil%20and%20the%20normalisation%20of%20bigotry%2C%20immorality%2C%20and%20lies%20that%20has%20become%20so%20prominent%20in%20our%20country%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20kids%20were%20exposed%20to%20bigoted%20ideas%20and%20misinformation%20even%20in%20the%20past.%20I%20remember%20some%20of%20my%20schoolmates%20and%20collegemates%20harbouring%20baseless%20ideas%20and%20making%20false%20claims%20about%20history%2C%20often%20exposed%20to%20those%20through%20parents%20and%20other%20relatives%20who%20were%20close%20to%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20numerous%20Hindutva%20organisations%20that%20dot%20our%20country.%20However%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20kids%20(like%20me)%20whose%20parents%20were%20too%20busy%20making%20ends%20meet%20to%20bother%20themselves%20with%20chest-thumping%20and%20%E2%80%9Creviving%E2%80%9D%20imaginary%20past%20glories%2C%20there%20were%20multiple%20layers%20of%20checks%20and%20balances%20in%20those%20days%2C%20especially%20in%20mainstream%20literature%20and%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20while%20I%20remember%20reading%20about%20and%20watching%20news%20on%20communal%20riots%20and%20murders%20throughout%20my%20childhood%2C%20I%20cannot%20think%20of%20any%20mainstream%20discourse%20in%20which%20the%20killings%20were%20justified%20and%20the%20murderers%20glorified.%20Patriotic%20TV%20shows%20and%20films%20were%20almost%20always%20inclusive%20(even%20if%2C%20as%20I%20realised%20later%2C%20the%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20representation%20was%20often%20paternalistic%20and%20the%20representation%20of%20Bahujan%20castes%20and%20groups%20almost%20absent).%20One%20of%20the%20most%20striking%20things%20I%20remember%20reading%20is%20a%20long%20article%20on%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20pogrom%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20was%20a%20highly%20detailed%20analysis%20and%20I%20learned%20several%20gory%20details%20of%20the%20violence.%20The%20article%20did%20not%2C%20however%2C%20make%20me%20start%20hating%20any%20broad%20religious%20or%20caste-based%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20I%20just%20ended%20up%20feeling%20immense%20anger%20towards%20the%20actual%20perpetrators%20of%20the%20violence%20as%20well%20as%20their%20political%20and%20bureaucratic%20enablers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848-1024x683.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848-1024x683.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06100716%2FIMG_6848.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-661861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20even%20a%20regular%20news%20report%20on%20something%20like%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20often%20ends%20up%20making%20young%20folks%20start%20labelling%20ordinary%20Indians%20as%20terrorists%20and%20traitors.%20Kids%20now%20are%20regularly%20coming%20across%20twisted%20takes%20on%20violence%20on%20every%20platform%2C%20often%20high%20up%20in%20search%20results%20and%20%E2%80%98Suggested%20Videos%2FArticles%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20well%20as%20during%20dinner%20time%20on%20mainstream%20TV%20channels.%20Then%20there%20are%20parents%20who%20are%20proudly%20teaching%20kids%20to%20sing%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20go%20shoot%20and%20kill%20the%20traitor%20bastards%E2%80%9D.%20More%20shockingly%2C%20this%20is%20all%20happening%20even%20as%20our%20education%20system%20is%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fmore-that-half-14-18-year-olds-in-rural-india-cannot-do-simple-division-aser-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eabsolute%20shambles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20lucky%20to%20have%20gone%20to%20a%20school%20with%20brilliant%20teachers%20and%20a%20well-run%20administration%2C%20and%20overall%20to%20have%20grown%20up%20during%20a%20period%20when%20mainstream%20media%20was%20generally%20serious%20about%20realistic%20analyses%20of%20the%20many%20broken%20systems%20in%20the%20country%20including%20education.%20Today%20we%20are%20at%20a%20stage%20when%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20the%20mainstream%20elite%20together%20are%20both%20robbing%20millions%20of%20kids%20of%20good%20educational%20opportunities%20in%20formal%20institutional%20spaces%2C%20as%20well%20as%20encouraging%20their%20mis-education%20via%20other%20spaces%2C%20most%20significantly%20the%20propaganda-suffused%20social%20media%20discourse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20wanton%20spread%20of%20misinformation%2C%20the%20normalisation%20of%20twisted%20morals%2C%20and%20the%20disdain%20for%20critical%20and%20intellectual%20rigor%2C%20all%20continue%20with%20the%20same%20zeal%20and%20speed%20as%20is%20happening%20today%2C%20with%20kids%20growing%20up%20in%20such%20a%20toxic%20cultural%20environment%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20long%20before%20we%20become%20a%20country%20mostly%20peopled%20by%20individuals%20whose%20minds%20are%20suffused%20with%20bigoted%20concepts%20and%20bereft%20of%20any%20logical%20thinking%20skills.%20We%20will%20become%20a%20country%20peopled%20by%2C%20well%2C%20%E2%80%98bigidiots%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20will%20see%20(and%20are%20indeed%20already%20seeing)%20more%20and%20more%20individuals%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20appreciate%20basic%20moral%20ideas%20like%20justice%20and%20equality%2C%20and%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20distinguish%20between%20reality%20and%20lies.%20We%20will%20become%20a%20nation%20whose%20gullible%20public%20can%20be%20easily%20goaded%20to%20believe%20that%20their%20lives%20and%20their%20country%20are%20being%20%E2%80%98destroyed%E2%80%99%20by%20Muslims%20and%20leftists%20and%20feminists%20and%20farmers%20and%20whatnot%2C%20even%20as%20politicians%2C%20news%20anchors%2C%20diaspora%20Indians%2C%20film%20actors%2C%20industrialists%20and%20other%20elites%20all%20take%20us%20for%20a%20royal%20ride.%20As%20some%20brave%2C%20smaller%20media%20platforms%20in%20our%20country%20have%20been%20reporting%20for%20years%2C%20relaying%20hateful%20propaganda%20has%20become%20a%20highly%20profitable%20business%20venture%20for%20the%20elites%20and%20%E2%80%98influencers%E2%80%99%20in%20India%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20cunningly%20sending%20their%20kids%20and%20loved%20ones%20either%20out%20of%20the%20country%20or%20into%20the%20protective%20higher%20echelons%20of%20the%20current%20ecosystem%2C%20even%20as%20they%20poison%20the%20discourse%20and%20the%20social%20fabric%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20hundreds%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20learning%20in%20school%20that%20the%20lotus%20flower%20blooms%20best%20in%20dirt%20and%20filth.%20If%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20world%20is%20any%20measure%2C%20that%20certainly%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20case%3A%20there%20is%20filth%20all%20around%2C%20and%20a%20few%20political%20and%20%E2%80%98cultural%E2%80%99%20organisations%20are%20thriving%20even%20as%20the%20public%20leaps%20from%20one%20crisis%20to%20the%20next.%20A%20particularly%20worrying%20consequence%20of%20this%20pervasive%20dirt%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20kids%20and%20teenagers%20are%20being%20constantly%20exposed%20to%20intellectual%20garbage.%20It%20is%20not%20hard%20to%20conclude%20that%20when%20they%20become%20adults%2C%20many%20(or%20most)%20of%20them%20might%20lack%20basic%20decency%20and%20compassion%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fundamental%20logical%20thinking%20skills.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGarbage%20in%2C%20garbage%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20they%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20is%2C%20until%20we%20acknowledge%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20toxic%20state%20of%20our%20nation%20and%20resolve%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20filth%20and%20throw%20out%20the%20poisonous%20lotuses%20being%20powered%20by%20it.%20We%20have%20to%20work%2C%20with%20all%20our%20might%2C%20towards%20a%20garbage-mukt%20Bharat%3A%20a%20newer%20India%20where%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egoli%20maaro%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E-type%20toxicity%20is%20neither%20normalised%20nor%20rewarded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fkkumbhar%2F%5C%22%3EKiran%20Kumbhar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20currently%20studying%20the%20history%20of%20science%20at%20Harvard%20University%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20history%20of%20medicine%20in%20modern%20India.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20physician%20and%20a%20health%20policy%20graduate.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710935458000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F02142235%2FIMG_0750-e1643792690720.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnew-india-and-the-reign-of-bigidiocy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20have%20to%20work%2C%20with%20all%20our%20might%2C%20towards%20a%20garbage-