20We%20think%20they%20are%20primitive%20and%20live%20in%20jungles.%20But%20when%20you%20read%20the%20proposals%2C%20you%20learn%20their%20diverse%20wisdom%2C%20culture%20and%20history.%20Through%20this%20fellowship%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20preserve%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Oinam%20Doren%2C%20a%20jury%20member%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20Samvaad%20fellows%202023%20include%20%E2%80%94%20Saka%20Mashangva%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344734%2Ftata-samvaad-jamshedpur-sumanti-devi-artisan-preserves-oraon-art-mud-natural-finger-painting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efolk%20artist%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20Tingteila%2C%20a%20traditional%20musical%20instrument%20of%20the%20Tangkhul%20tribe%20of%20Manipur%20which%20is%20almost%20extinct%3B%20Santosh%20Pawar%2C%20a%20social%20activist%20who%20wants%20to%20preserve%20and%20promote%20the%20folklore%20of%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%3B%20Madhavi%20Meravi%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20the%20folk%20tales%20of%20Gond%20tribal%20communities%20as%20part%20of%20children%E2%80%99s%20literature%3B%20Pansy%20Jami%2C%20who%20wants%20to%20document%20the%20benefits%20of%20fermented%20food%20from%20the%20Lotha%20Naga%20tribe%20of%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20applicants%20who%20get%20rejected%20are%20encouraged%20to%20apply%20again%2C%20shared%20Oinam.%20The%20jury%20members%20and%20Samvaad%20team%20continue%20to%20provide%20support%20by%20staying%20in%20touch%20to%20help%20participants%20enhance%20their%20ideas%20or%20pitches%20for%20a%20stronger%20comeback.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%3A%20Samvaad%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710425627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FWancho_language_training_of_teacher_PC_banwang_losu-1710425245.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20tribal%20communities%20have%20been%20witnessing%20their%20cultures%20fade.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20fellowship%20programme%20is%20empowering%20tribal%20youth%20to%20use%20the%20tools%20of%20modernity%20to%20protect%20their%20indigenous%20heritage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Gopi%20Karelia%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344880%2Ftata-samvaad-steel-foundation-fellowship-tribal-youth-empowerment-culture-preservation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224000%2B%20People%20Are%20Getting%20Life-Saving%20Dialysis%20Through%20This%20Amazing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakala%20Devi%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%20from%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Chamoli%20district%2C%20started%20experiencing%20severe%20body%20pain%2C%20fever%2C%20chills%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20difficulty%20walking%20in%20late%202021.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20her%20work%20in%20her%20district%2C%20these%20symptoms%20caused%20her%20considerable%20discomfort%20and%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20continue%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20visited%20nearby%20doctors%20and%20PHCs%2C%20who%20ordered%20some%20basic%20tests%20and%20prescribed%20medicines.%20After%20two%20weeks%20of%20rest%20at%20home%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20did%20not%20experience%20any%20improvement.%20A%20doctor%20advised%20her%20to%20visit%20a%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%20for%20better%20access%20to%20treatment%2C%20which%20involved%20travelling%20almost%20four%20hours%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%20over%20150%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Government-aided%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Chandrakala%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140950%2Findian-scientists-develop-sensor-for-early-detection-of-chronic-kidney-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20kidney%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advised%20dialysis%20twice%20a%20week.%20As%20this%20treatment%20was%20not%20available%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20she%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20two%20nights%20every%20week%20to%20get%20the%20dialysis%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20single%20mother%2C%20being%20separated%20from%20her%20son%2C%20spending%20on%20travel%2C%20and%20eight%20nights%20at%20lodging%20every%20month%2C%20was%20much%20more%20than%20what%20she%20could%20afford%2C%20both%20physically%20and%20mentally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20faced%20by%20the%20ASHA%20worker%20resonates%20with%20many%20residing%20in%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGlobal%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20(GBD)%202015%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Chronic%20Kidney%20Disease%20(CKD)%20ranks%20as%20the%20eighth%20leading%20cause%20of%20death%20in%20India%2C%20largely%20because%20many%20patients%20develop%20complications%20leading%20to%20end-stage%20renal%20disease.%20A%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Lancet%3C%2Fem%3E%20estimated%20that%20two%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20develop%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20every%20year%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250227%2Fshashank-moddhia-mumbai-startup-renal-project-affordable-kidney-dialysis-in-india-healthcare-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20long-term%20dialysis%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20dialysis%20care%20add%20to%20the%20financial%20woes%20of%20patients.%20Collaborating%20with%20the%20Uttarakhand%20Government%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20(THF)%20identified%20renal%20care%20as%20a%20major%20gap.%20Noticing%20that%20many%20residents%20in%20hilly%20areas%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20Dehradun%20or%20Haldwani%20for%20dialysis%2C%20the%20organisation%20decided%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap%20by%20establishing%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20throughout%20the%20state%2C%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20with%20a%20single%20centre%20in%20March%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20over%2027%20centres%20across%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Punjab.%20Over%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20THF%20has%20helped%20over%204%2C000%20patients%20access%20free%20dialysis%20through%20these%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201188px)%20100vw%2C%201188px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221188%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20established%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20throughout%20the%20state%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627.jpg%201188w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627-300x156.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627-500x260.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627-768x400.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FScreenshot-2024-03-14-093810_11zon-1710411627-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344875%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22618%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20established%20the%20last-mile%20availability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20rural%20areas%20through%20the%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20initiative.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImproving%20access%20to%20dialysis%20in%20remote%20areas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Government%20report%20has%20indicated%20an%20additional%20demand%20for%203.4%20crore%20dialysis%20procedures%20annually.%20However%2C%20the%20predominantly%20private%20dialysis%20centres%20cater%20to%20less%20than%20half%20of%20this%20demand%2C%20making%20them%20unaffordable%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F141684%2Fkamal-shahs-medical-problem-inspired-him-entrepreneur-nephroplus-dialysis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatients%20in%20need%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Government%20initiated%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Program%20(PMNDP)%20in%202016%2C%20operating%20under%20a%20Public-Private%20Partnership%20(PPP)%20model%20to%20offer%20free%20dialysis%20services%20to%20economically%20disadvantaged%20individuals.%20This%20programme%20encompasses%20both%20hemodialysis%20and%20peritoneal%20dialysis%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Government%20to%20ensure%20free%20dialysis%20care%20in%20areas%20where%20this%20essential%20healthcare%20service%20isn%E2%80%99t%20available.%20Each%20centre%20is%20staffed%20with%20a%20medical%20officer%2C%20a%20technician%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20and%20a%20housekeeping%20staff%2C%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20three%20dialysis%20machines.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20nephrologist%20is%20assigned%20to%20each%20centre%2C%20who%20makes%20monthly%20visits%20and%20is%20available%20for%20consultations%20and%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20renal%20care%20centres%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%20and%20are%20located%20within%20the%20Government%20district%20and%20zonal%20hospitals.%20While%20the%20space%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20THF%20provides%20the%20necessary%20staffing%2C%20machines%2C%20medicines%2C%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20centres%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%2C%20THF%20also%20operates%20a%20few%20private%20and%20independent%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%2C%20which%20provide%20cost-effective%20and%20subsidised%20dialysis%20care%20to%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20over%2064%2C000%20dialysis%20sessions%20have%20been%20conducted%20across%20the%2030%20centres%2C%20with%2028%20of%20them%20operating%20in%20partnership%20with%20different%20State%20Governments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20remaining%20two%20are%20privately%20managed%20by%20the%20foundation.%20The%20private%20centres%2C%20present%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Punjab%2C%20offer%20dialysis%20at%20subsidised%20rates.%20The%20foundation%20is%20also%20soon%20planning%20to%20expand%20to%20even%20more%20centres%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20State%20Governments%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20Punjab%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%20like%20Chandrakala%2C%20this%20is%20a%20boon%2C%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20time%2C%20energy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20money.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20had%20to%20spend%20two%20days%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20which%20posed%20a%20major%20challenge%20due%20to%20travelling%2C%20especially%20considering%20I%20reside%20in%20a%20hilly%20area%20with%20rugged%20terrain.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20have%20no%20one%20to%20accompany%20me%20as%20my%20son%20attends%20college.%20Enduring%20this%20commute%20for%20almost%20four%20months%20left%20me%20exhausted%20and%20made%20work%20exceedingly%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centre%20opened%20its%20doors%20in%20Karnaprayag%2C%20a%20mere%20half-hour%20journey%20from%20Chandrakala%E2%80%99s%20residence.%20This%20reduced%20her%20travel%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20she%20could%20return%20home%20within%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20day%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20promptly%20fulfil%20her%20duties%20as%20an%20ASHA%20worker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20kidney%20health%3A%20dialysis%2C%20costs%2C%20and%20access%20initiatives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHealthy%20kidneys%20cleanse%20your%20blood%2C%20removing%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%20from%20your%20body%20in%20the%20form%20of%20urine.%20They%20also%20regulate%20acidity%20levels%20and%20contribute%20to%20maintaining%20a%20proper%20balance%20of%20water%2C%20salts%2C%20and%20minerals%20in%20your%20bloodstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20kidneys%20are%20unable%20to%20remove%20enough%20wastes%20and%20fluids%20from%20the%20blood%2C%20it%20causes%20a%20build-up%20of%20toxins%20and%20waste.%20Dialysis%20replaces%20the%20functions%20of%20the%20kidney%20by%20removing%20the%20waste%20and%20excess%20fluid%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Ganpat%20Ram%2C%20Medical%20Officer%20at%20Karnaprayag%20Renal%20Care%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22THF's%20program%20aims%20to%20provide%20quality%20dialysis%20services%20to%20people%20in%20remote%20areas%2C%20reducing%20costs%20and%20travel%20time%20to%20improve%20their%20well-being.%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FTier-4-1847_11zon-1710411623-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploa